{"tid":1490078,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無諗過做條警方使用過份武力timeline係facebook ig等洗版?","createTime":"2019-08-20T04:23:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T04:32:55.000Z","uid":294199,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b44ff7c5ac3f841f0ff3b7f8ea4c1ff56cd4d89f","tid":1490078,"uid":294199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:23:14.000Z","msg":"想整合一條警方使用過份武力timeline,係facebook等地方瘋狂洗版<br />\ntimeline內容格式以文字為先<br />\n<br />\n例如:<br />\n12/6/2019 警方向示威者頭部開槍，示威者險失明。<br />\n(<a href=\"http://www.圖片.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.%E5%9C%96%E7%89%87.jpg&d=QZ1X7Ww%2BB3pe%2FYPW%2Fe6VuTaf%2B7McJKZiP%2F5rhSwlYLA%3D&h=5e537af9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.圖片.jpg</a>)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>做timeline目的最主要有兩個，唔用網頁主要係因為fb ig係主流</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n1.等淺藍封口／對中立更了解咩事，可能仲有人加入／對自家重睇一次可以令怒火返翻黎<br />\n2.我相信下一次前線行動應該會再升級,升級前重溫同推廣timeline有助固定現有民意...甚至引入更多前線<br />\n<br />\n其實我好想親手自己做唔靠兄弟,但本身有工作,放假都出左黎玩online,一個人係短時間內整合唔到2個月既timeline.<br />\n<br />\n所以希望各兄弟一齊幫幫手!"},{"pid":"f032f6ab9c6ed82d20da53aa99182a203c67e55d","tid":1490078,"uid":40356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:25:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e9624d7b697aa33dd2bdb7313de9bf3250a8e8c8","tid":1490078,"uid":294199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:32:55.000Z","msg":"我P牌推唔到.幫幫手"}]}